attributes.title: "Danger on the Dirt" brings fans inside the minds of bull riders
attributes.description: “From the time I was little, my dad told me, ‘You play the game, you take the pain.’ I’ve always tried to live by that,” said J.B. Mauney in a PBR one-hour CBS special that airs on Dec. 27.
